export const clockColors: { [key: string]: string } = {
  colorWhenUsedForHoursAndMinutes:      'rgb(101, 199, 97)',     // dark olive green
  colorWhenUsedForHours :               'rgb(57, 80, 2)', // olive green
  colorWhenUsedForMinutes:              'rgb(50, 116, 49)',     // light olive green
  colorWhenNotUsed:                     'rgb(64, 161, 87)',   // light olive green
  clockBackGroundColorArrayStartColor:  'rgb(49,71,1)',   // Emerald Green
  clockBackGroundColorArrayEndColor:    'rgb(49, 71, 1)',    // Emerald Green
  secondsCounterArrayStartColor:        'rgb(101, 199, 97)',    // light olive green
  secondsCounterArrayEndColor:          'rgb(64, 161, 87)'     //  light olive green
}
